Real Madrid beat Atletico Madrid 3-1 in the Champions League semi-final second leg on Wednesday night . 
  Sergio Ramos was deployed in midfield after Luka Modric was injured . 
  The defender could play in every position on the pitch for Carlo Ancelotti's side . 
  Ramos is Real Madrid's Carles Puyol and has proved his worth to the club . 
  The centre-back scored the winning goal in the Bernabeu . 
 